name: Nova Diretriz
description: Ad Hoc Orquestra is a project based on collective improvisation, creating music in real time and promoting the encounter between multiple artists. Nova Diretriz was created and recorded live by Bruna Vilela (guitar), Camila Rocha (bass), Lúcia Vulcano (guitar), Luisa Mitre (keyboard), Natália Mitre (drums), Paige (voice) and the conductor Guilherme Peluci. Recorded at Studio Bioma in 2019 by Pedro Cambraia and Mixed by Marc Urselli. Released in July 31 2020. https://adhocorquestra.bandcamp.com/
